OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOutbreaks of rain through the
OL,6,Fmorning with the odd brighter
OL,7,Finterval. Further, locally heavy, rain
OL,8,Fexpected early afternoon. Rain and
OL,9,Fcloud clearing later to deliver a
OL,10,Ffine, sunny evening for most. Winds
OL,11,Fremain blustery throughout.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FPlenty of late sunshine for
OL,14,Fmost under clearing skies, with winds
OL,15,Feasing. One or two blustery showers
OL,16,Fpossible into the hours of darkness,
OL,17,Fdry and clear after midnight. Chilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
